  <description type="morphology">Plants perennial, glabrous. Stems prostrate, forming mats to 2 m diam., branched;
        rooting at nodes. Leaves: petiole ± absent; blade oblanceolate to elliptic-ovate, to 6 × 2.5
        cm, tapered to clasping base. Inflorescences: flowers solitary; pedicel to 20 mm. Flowers:
        calyx lobes pink-purple adaxially, with subapical abaxial appendages, ovate to lanceolate,
        3–10 mm; stamens 30; pistil 5-carpellate; ovary 5-loculed; styles 5. Capsules conic, 10 mm.
        Seeds 30–60, black, 1.2–1.5 mm, shiny, smooth.</description>
